# Repo Boundary Rule

## Core principle
- This repository is the single source of truth for `switch-env`.
- `~/bin` is runtime output only. Do not treat `~/bin` files as source files.

## Required behavior
- Only edit source in this repository directory.
- Use installer flow to publish runtime files into `~/bin`.
- Keep `.zshrc` out of repository scope.

## Forbidden behavior
- Do not copy random files from `~/bin` into this repository.
- Do not commit machine-local cache/state files.
- Do not commit secrets, tokens, or credentials.

## Excluded from repository
- `~/.zshrc`
- `.venv`, `.switch-py-cache`, local runtime caches
- Any API tokens or private keys
